{"tid":2125892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何猷啟數月前已辦離婚    與妻性格不合而分開","createTime":"2020-07-26T13:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T13:39:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea04cf978d1e2410afd39ccec2f93715691fc935","tid":2125892,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cloCwBzNWumVstSOBUVIlw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-07/56ce8cd0-cf03-11ea-be6e-a8021e786fa5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FcloCwBzNWumVstSOBUVIlw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-07%2F56ce8cd0-cf03-11ea-be6e-a8021e786fa5&h=52d753cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已故賭王何鴻燊兒子、已婚的何猷啟昨日驚爆背妻偷食，認識一位年約20歲嘅少女Alice Chung，即傳言四起指二人交往已有一段時間，更指猷啟帶女方與自己的朋友唱K見面等。據知，猷啟與太太齊嬌（Gigi）在數月前已辦離婚手續，二人因性格不合而分開，因此猷啟認識新女友後，亦公開帶女友與朋友聚會。<br />\n<br />\n猷啟與齊嬌即使離婚，仍會以一對女兒為大前提，而二人分開亦與早前傳出的婆媳關係欠佳無關。雖然二人早有分開之意，但當時礙於賭王健康不佳，雙方均認為不是宣布的理想時候。賭王5月離世後，齊嬌始終是猷啟兩女的母親，加上何氏家族顯赫，因此在賭王離世的訃聞及喪禮上，仍視齊嬌為何家媳婦。"},{"pid":"84d23e426a06351bd0d6cbb2261e8ccbb2015550","tid":2125892,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:38:15.000Z","msg":"巴打有機會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bb15a999b690c24cac247c1ea09c96125ecbff","tid":2125892,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T13:39:07.000Z","msg":"與妻子個閪不合姐<br />\n<br />\n分完身家咪可以離婚囉"}]}